return ['messages'=>['<p>At the heart of the Parfum lies a special-cut citrine, celebrated for its vibrant golden hue and unparalleled clarity. This semi-precious stone, with its sleek, flowing lines, is a modern interpretation of feminine grace and strength. The meticulous craftsmanship extends beyond to the special cutting of the citrine, ensuring each unique facet reflects light in a way that evokes the silhouette of a woman. The golden hue of the 18K Yellow Gold setting complements the citrine, enhancing the radiant essence of this jewellery creation.</p>'=>'<p>「香水瓶」（Parfum）以一顆特裁黃水晶為核心，其鮮明的金黃色澤與無瑕透明度令人讚歎。這顆半寶石以流暢線條勾勒，展現女性的優雅與堅韌。精湛的切割工藝使每一個切面折射光芒，勾勒出柔美輪廓。18K黃金與黃水晶相得益彰，進一步突顯其高雅神韻。   </p>','<p>Come and celebrate the return of a classic with us! Experience our bespoke service, which allows you to customize your Parfum piece, making this legacy jewellery creation truly one-of-a-kind.</p>'=>'<p>與我們一起慶祝經典之作的回歸！體驗我們的定製服務，定製您獨一無二的專屬Parfum。 </p>','<p>In the world of fine jewellery, every creation tells a story, weaving together threads of inspiration, craftsmanship, and timeless design. The Parfum is no exception. This exquisite jewellery creation draws its inspiration from the serene beauty of a contemporary muse, gracefully draped in a glittering gold dress on a grand theatre stage. The Parfum embodies the quintessence – luxury, sophistication and the infinite femininity of a beautiful modern lady.</p>'=>'<p>在高級珠寶的世界中，每件作品都在訴說一段故事，交織靈感、工藝與雋永設計。EJI「香水瓶」（Parfum）亦不例外。這款精緻珠寶從現代謬思的靜謐之美汲取靈感，彷彿一位身著閃耀金色禮服的女子，優雅站立於華麗劇院舞台中央。它凝聚奢華、精緻與現代女性無盡魅力的精髓。   </p>','<p>Sophistication in craftsmanship is evident in every detail of the Parfum. The design and special cutting of the citrine stand out with precision, preserving the gemstone’s beauty and unique reflective qualities. This attention to detail transforms our talented designer’s initial inspiration into a paragon of elegance, capturing the essence of femininity and redefining what it means to be truly elegant. Every aspect of this jewellery creation reflects our dedication to excellence as a fine jewellery manufacturer.</p>'=>'<p>「香水瓶」（Parfum）每一處細節皆彰顯精湛工藝。黃水晶設計與特裁手法精準無瑕，保留寶石的天然美感與獨特反射特性。這種對細節的極致追求，將設計師的靈感化為優雅，捕捉女性魅力本質，重新定義真正的典雅。每個環節，皆體現我們作為高級珠寶製造商對卓越的執著。   </p>','<p>This September, at the prestigious JGW, the Parfum made its grand return, ready to captivate and enchant audiences once more. The Parfum has been one of our iconic collections for more than ten years, standing as a testament to our commitment to excellence and timeless design. Embracing its radiant beauty, the Parfum shines brilliantly, ready to illuminate your journey.</p><p>Discover the Parfum and welcome its return to the spotlight, mesmerizing the world with its stunning beauty and sophistication. Embrace the legacy of this forever icon, where it tells a story of elegance, luxury and timeless beauty.</p>'=>'<p>今年九月，Parfum於享譽盛名的JGW展會華麗回歸，再度以其魅力征服觀眾。作為我們逾十年的標誌性系列，Parfum見證了品牌對雋永設計的承諾。其耀眼光芒閃爍，準備照亮您的旅程。  </p><p>誠邀您探索Parfum，迎接它重返鎂光燈下的重要時刻。 </p>','A Gem of Inspiration'=>'靈感之寶石','A Return to Classic'=>'經典回歸','Craftsmanship Beyond Excellence'=>'卓越的工藝','Follow Us '=>'關注我們  ','editor-text-editor-461114d'=>'<p>今年九月，Parfum於享譽盛名的JGW展會華麗回歸，再度以其魅力征服觀眾。作為我們逾十年的標誌性系列，Parfum見證了品牌對雋永設計的承諾。其耀眼光芒閃爍，準備照亮您的旅程。  </p><p>誠邀您探索Parfum，迎接它重返鎂光燈下的重要時刻。 </p>','editor-text-editor-691aa82'=>'<p>在高級珠寶的世界中，每件作品都在訴說一段故事，交織靈感、工藝與雋永設計。EJI「香水瓶」（Parfum）亦不例外。這款精緻珠寶從現代謬思的靜謐之美汲取靈感，彷彿一位身著閃耀金色禮服的女子，優雅站立於華麗劇院舞台中央。它凝聚奢華、精緻與現代女性無盡魅力的精髓。   </p>','editor-text-editor-843d631'=>'<p>「香水瓶」（Parfum）每一處細節皆彰顯精湛工藝。黃水晶設計與特裁手法精準無瑕，保留寶石的天然美感與獨特反射特性。這種對細節的極致追求，將設計師的靈感化為優雅，捕捉女性魅力本質，重新定義真正的典雅。每個環節，皆體現我們作為高級珠寶製造商對卓越的執著。   </p>','editor-text-editor-b7e2ae6'=>'<p>與我們一起慶祝經典之作的回歸！體驗我們的定製服務，定製您獨一無二的專屬Parfum。 </p>','editor-text-editor-ed67bef'=>'<p>「香水瓶」（Parfum）以一顆特裁黃水晶為核心，其鮮明的金黃色澤與無瑕透明度令人讚歎。這顆半寶石以流暢線條勾勒，展現女性的優雅與堅韌。精湛的切割工藝使每一個切面折射光芒，勾勒出柔美輪廓。18K黃金與黃水晶相得益彰，進一步突顯其高雅神韻。   </p>','title-heading-0393b6f'=>'經典回歸','title-heading-09233f7'=>'靈感之寶石','title-heading-552ae02'=>'關注我們  ','title-heading-a60c794'=>'卓越的工藝']];
